                            - Harmony IDB -
================================================================================


1.) Edit the service properties: resources/properties/hsi.properties
2.) Add dir.webapps to build.local.properties

Local testing:
==============
 * test.properties: test.callWebservice = false
 * idb.properties: passViaWebservice = false
 * Also you could remove the harmony-adapter-dummy.jar file and link the adapter
   project within eclipse for better debugging.

Webservice testing:
==================
 * test.properties: test.callWebservice = true
 * idb.properties: passViaWebservice = true
